OL,3,CScot who refused to abandon
OL,4,Cschoolgirls to the Nazis honoured with
OL,5,Cnew plaques
OL,7,FA Scottish missionary who was murdered
OL,8,Fby the Nazis after caring for Jewish
OL,9,Fschoolgirls in Budapest has been
OL,10,Fhonoured with new memorials in her
OL,11,Fadopted city, the Church of Scotland
OL,12,Fhas announced.
OL,14,FJane Haining, who grew up on a farm
OL,15,Fnear Dunscore in Dumfriesshire, worked
OL,16,Fas a matron at the Scottish Mission
OL,17,FSchool in the Hungarian capital from
OL,18,F1932 to 1944, before being arrested on
OL,19,Fcharges that included working among
OL,20,FJews, and weeping when seeing girls
OL,21,Fattend class wearing yellow stars.
