OL,7,FOn May 14 1944, the 47-year-old was
OL,8,Ftransported to the Auschwitz-Birkenau
OL,9,Fconcentration camp in occupied Poland
OL,10,Fwhere she is likely to have been
OL,11,Fforced to undertake slave labour
OL,12,Fbefore dying on July 17 1944.
