OL,7,FAt a ceremony last Thursday, exactly
OL,8,F80 years after she was arrested, two
OL,9,Fmemorials were unveiled outside St
OL,10,FColumba's Church of Scotland in
OL,11,FBudapest where the school was located:
OL,12,Fa "Stolperstein" or brass plaque
OL,13,Fembedded in the pavement, and a plaque
OL,14,Fcommemorating Ms Haining and school
OL,15,Fheadteacher Margit Prem.
