OL,7,FThe Rev Ian Alexander, who leads on
OL,8,Finternational partnerships for the
OL,9,Fchurch, said: "We are delighted that a
OL,10,Fnew plaque and stolperstein has been
OL,11,Funveiled outside the church in honour
OL,12,Fof Jane Haining and her friend and
OL,13,Fcolleague Margit Prem.
OL,15,F"Both women showed tremendous courage
OL,16,Fin the face of intolerable evil during
OL,17,Fa dark period of history.
