OL,4,Cschoolgirls to the Nazis honoured with
OL,5,Cnew plaques
OL,7,F"Miss Haining was fully aware of the
OL,8,Frisks she was taking but repeatedly
OL,9,Frefused to leave Budapest and return
OL,10,Fhome to Scotland as the war engulfed
OL,11,FEurope.
OL,13,F"She was determined to continue doing
OL,14,Fher duty and stick to her post, saying
OL,15,F'If these children need me in days of
OL,16,Fsunshine, how much more do they need
OL,17,Fme in days of darkness?'
