OL,5,Cnew plaques
OL,7,F"Miss Haining was simultaneously an
OL,8,Fordinary and extraordinary woman and
OL,9,Fher inspirational story is one of
OL,10,Fheroism, personal sacrifice and
OL,11,Fheartbreak, reminding us that when we
OL,12,Ffeel powerless, there is always
OL,13,Fsomething that we can do."
