OL,7,FThe ceremony was attended by three of
OL,8,Fthe school's former pupils, along with
OL,9,Fa rabbi and deputy mayor Szilvia
OL,10,FBenedikta Temesvari, who gave a speech
OL,11,Fhighlighting the injustice of the
OL,12,Fcrimes with which Ms Haining was
OL,13,Fcharged, and the importance of
OL,14,Ftolerance.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/10
