OL,4,Cschoolgirls to the Nazis honoured with
OL,5,Cnew plaques
OL,7,FThe Rev Aaron Stevens, minister of St
OL,8,FColumba's Church of Scotland, said:
OL,9,F"There are other plaques to Jane
OL,10,FHaining in the world (and) there is a
OL,11,Fbust commemorating Margit Prem and a
OL,12,Fpark named after her, but this is only
OL,13,Fmemorial to the two of them together.
OL,15,F"When the Scottish Mission School
OL,16,Fopened here, Margit Prem was the
OL,17,Fprincipal of the school.
OL,19,F"Later, when they took Jane Haining
OL,20,Faway, it was the end of an era for
OL,21,Fthat school which was closed.
