OL,4,Cschoolgirls to the Nazis honoured with
OL,5,Cnew plaques
OL,7,F"They were friends, together they made
OL,8,Fthe school what it was, and in many
OL,9,Fways both of them dedicated their
OL,10,Flives to this school."
OL,12,FThere are more than 75,000
OL,13,FStolpersteine memorials across Europe
OL,14,Foutside the homes of, or places
OL,15,Fassociated with, victims of the Nazi
OL,16,FHolocaust.
OL,18,FMs Haining's bravery in protecting the
OL,19,Fchildren in her care previously saw
OL,20,Fher awarded a Heroine of the Holocaust
OL,21,Fmedal by the UK Government.
